title: [Ta'Illistim, Cobbled Walkway]
description: Pale interlocking stones are joined together to create a cobbled walkway that leads up to an ornate mistwood gate set into a low greystone wall.  Fragrant bushes of blooming alabaster roses line either side of the entrance, their light petals standing out against the dark background.

Diffuse moonlight illuminates the pale interlocking stones of a cobbled walkway  that leads up to an ornate mistwood gate set into a low greystone wall. Fragrant bushes of blooming alabaster roses line either side of the entrance, their light petals highlighted by the soft luminescence from above.
